Implement strictly the rules, regulations and processes in the release of checks;
Prepare the RCI and submit the same to the AO along with the complete paid DVs and other supporting documents;
Head, AO,  to inform the TO with their discrepancies, particularly the unrecorded disbursements in the MBRS; and
